Question: Write a summary (plot synopsis) of your favorite movie.
Answer:
My favorite movie is Pride and Prejudice by Jane Austin. It revolves around an inteligent young girl who is very strong minded. She is introduced to a vwry wealthy and shy man. At first his shyness is interpreted as arrogance but later the young girl come to find out what a kind and gentle fellow he is. She develops feelings for him and he does the same and soon they get engaged regardless of their social statuses and external forces of opposition. 